Description: A blockr dock board (DAG, assistant and markdown document panes,
    with board persistence) deployed to Posit Connect for user acceptance
    testing, published via blockr.ci's connect-deploy (pull-mode) pipeline.
    Structured as an R package so the deploy workflow resolves its runtime
    dependencies from this DESCRIPTION.
